Name: DanielX.net Paint Composer
About the game: Do you like making music? If so DanielX.net Paint Composer is the perfect game to expand your creativity. The simple interface, versatile sounds, and fun characters will make all of your musical dreams come true. Compose songs effortlessly! Easily share your creations with the world by creating a link that anyone can follow to see and hear what you've come up with. Export your music as: .mp3, .wav, .midi. You can even export .mp4 videos to upload to your favorite video hosting platforms! Import songs from .midi files, use custom SoundFonts, create custom video effects, even use your own sprites and characters. There is no limit to what you can create! I hope you have as much fun playing with Paint Composer as I had making it. - Daniel X Moore
